00:36:38,150 --> 00:36:39,251
were running these simple games.

766
00:36:40,011 --> 00:36:41,673
Now it's almost exactly the reverse.

767
00:36:41,713 --> 00:36:43,674
Now we have these extremely detailed games,

768
00:36:44,835 --> 00:36:46,857
